### Docker run mysql
docker run --restart unless-stopped -p 3306:3306 --name mysql -e MYSQL_ROOT_HOST=% -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=root -e MYSQL_DATABASE=myschema -d mysql

docker run -it mysql bash

mysql -uroot -proot -h localhost -P 3306
mysql -uroot -proot -h 0.0.0.0 -P 3306





### Run configuration

# add spring instrument to CP on jvm with arg:
-javaagent:C:\Users\vkara\.m2\repository\org\springframework\spring-instrument\5.0.3.RELEASE\spring-instrument-5.0.3.RELEASE.jar

For jUnit, goo to Edit Configuration -> Default -> JUnit